{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)showsUserLocation","title":"showsUserLocation","fragments":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L590","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"}},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/showsUserLocation"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the map may display the user location."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/showsuserlocation"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Setting this property to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" causes the map view to use the Core Location"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"framework to find the current location. As long as this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"map view continues to track the user’s location and update it periodically."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property does not indicate whether the user’s position is actually visible"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on the map, only whether the map view is allowed to display it. To determine"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whether the user’s position is visible, use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocationVisible"},{"type":"text","text":" property."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Your app must specify a value for ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" in its "},{"code":"Info.plist","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to satisfy the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"requirements of the underlying Core Location framework when enabling this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you implement a custom location manager, set the "},{"code":"locationManager","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calling "},{"code":"showsUserLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapL